items.title: France, Vietnam sign Airbus, satellite deals as Macron visits Hanoi
items.description: France and Vietnam signed a deal on Monday for 20 Airbus planes, among other pacts, as President Emmanuel Macron visited Hanoi.

items.title: Trump delays 50% tariffs on EU to July 9
items.description: President of the European Commission Ursula Von der Leyen said that she had a "good call" with Trump, but needed until July 9 to "reach a good deal."

items.title: Sen. Ron Johnson says there are 'enough' GOP senators to stall House budget bill

items.title: House Speaker Johnson downplays deficit concerns as budget bill faces skeptics in Senate
items.description: Speaker Mike Johnson rejected concerns that the "big, beautiful bill" will add to the federal deficit.
